      <guid>https://example.com/p/go%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%8D%E5%88%B6map%E5%8F%AF%E8%83%BD%E9%81%87%E5%88%B0%E5%9D%91/</guid>
      <description>昨天下午遇到一个问题。服务A与服务B批量建立tcp连接，并定时发送rpc请求（rpc.Ping()）检查连接的健康状态。A服务在kibana出现报错：
use of closed network connection 第一反应是B服务重启导致连接断开，正好落在A服务检查出错与重连的时间窗口。运维同学帮拉日志，发现错误：
{&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;fatal error: concurrent map iteration and map write\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.771394863Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;[11/01/19 10:52:52] [DEBG] RouterRPC Put Request =\u003e \u0026{6076362058 1 200178629686 2fadfb7c24bb440cb9dfcb74f515baef server:1:currt:1572229900380812731:498081}\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stdout&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.771452423Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.773643972Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;goroutine 62906840 [running]:\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.773666216Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;runtime.throw(0x932fd7, 0x26)\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.773672033Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;\u0009/app/go1.9/go/src/runtime/panic.go:605 +0x95 fp=0xc4202019a8 sp=0xc420201988 pc=0x42d1a5\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.773676889Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;runtime.mapiternext(0xc420201ac8)\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.773682159Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;\u0009/app/go1.9/go/src/runtime/hashmap.go:778 +0x6f1 fp=0xc420201a40 sp=0xc4202019a8 pc=0x40b7c1\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.773686889Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;main.(*RouterRPC).AllRoomCount(0xc4201988c0, 0xc420b08630, 0xc420192158, 0x0, 0x0)\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.773694133Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;\u0009/path/to/project/rpc.go:185 +0x161 fp=0xc420201b38 sp=0xc420201a40 pc=0x809421\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.773704869Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;runtime.call64(0xc420187f20, 0xc420192078, 0xc420358b10, 0x1800000028)\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;time&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;2019-11-01T02:52:52.773713993Z&amp;#34;} {&amp;#34;log&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;\u0009/app/go1.9/go/src/runtime/asm_amd64.s:510 +0x3b fp=0xc420201b88 sp=0xc420201b38 pc=0x45b86b\n&amp;#34;,&amp;#34;stream&amp;#34;:&amp;#34;stderr&amp;#34;, ... 显示是并发读写map出错，看下这行代码：
